					<ul>
						<li>Indexes your local codebase to create searchable metadata</li>
						<li>Provides an MCP (Model Context Protocol) server for LLM integration</li>
						<li>Enables file-based context sharing with AI language models</li>
						<li>Operates entirely on your local machine</li>
					</ul>
